Subject: [PATCH 5.14 179/432] iio: dac: ad5624r: Fix incorrect handling of an optional regulator.
Date:   Thu, 16 Sep 2021 17:58:48 +0200
Message-Id: <20210916155816.805331940@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.33.0
